Company Overview of WiserTogether, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
WiserTogether, Inc. provides shared decision-making tools to consumers, employers, health plans, payers, and providers. Its decision-making tools enable consumers to achieve better health outcomes; and employers, health plans, and payers to save money. The company offers Wiser Health, a personalized decision-making tool that assesses possible treatments, and helps consumers to determine the best option for them based on various factors, including clinical evidence, personal and popular preferences, cost, and coverage; Wiser Health Mail, a hyper-targeted message that helps clients to engage consumers in their own health care decisions; and Wiser Health Social that uses social media to continu...
WiserTogether, Inc. provides shared decision-making tools to consumers, employers, health plans, payers, and providers. Its decision-making tools enable consumers to achieve better health outcomes; and employers, health plans, and payers to save money. The company offers Wiser Health, a personalized decision-making tool that assesses possible treatments, and helps consumers to determine the best option for them based on various factors, including clinical evidence, personal and popular preferences, cost, and coverage; Wiser Health Mail, a hyper-targeted message that helps clients to engage consumers in their own health care decisions; and Wiser Health Social that uses social media to continuously engage consumers on their health and wellness decisions. It offers its solutions in various health areas, including musculoskeletal and cardiovascular conditions, diabetes, mental health, pregnancy, and respiratory illnesses. WiserTogether, Inc. was founded in 2008 and is based in Washington, District Of Columbia with an additional office in Boston, Massachusetts.
